name: Journey of the local
description:
My life as a photographer make me able to explore some non-city places in Indonesia particularly. This photo taken in Sumba-NTT, Indonesia, one of the exotic place in Indonesia.

unsurprisingly, local in the non-city place have so much stamina than us as a comer. They are used to exploring their area even with their bare foot, make it a unique trait for the local.
